		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>A cleric that follows a religious practice dedicated to death, dying, or magic that corrupts life. Sometimes a reaper religion includes worship of undeath or necromancy, but sometimes it is a more benign faith that focuses on the peaceful and natural passage of life into death, or passage into an afterlife.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Reaper</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.XbGbZ2pHmxfse7uo]{Channel Divinity: Soul Tether}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.FihySMXtVPQBLHCJ]{Siphon Life}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8G8euVlVibbabs9L]{Draw Upon Vitality}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.lLzDS5oK69UvlRJ5]{Death Touched}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.oKEsTn9Jw7Whmyo9]{Corrupt Healing}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Cleric Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.TGKwq1txYa7Y4iIQ]{Inflict Wounds}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.43Vyt2wzU0SISfYm]{Rend Vigor}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Yp0dI1hIN0FPMGdH]{Spirit Link}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.cHIuORdoA1WnHfmK]{Well of Corruption}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.seKEwAbEZFBi6GWb]{Life Drain}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.izFZhMupYa9gH9c8]{Spectral Lance}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spe